5 General Assembly shall be for two years and the initial term of the other member appointed by
6 the General Assembly shall be for four years to be determined by lot at the first meeting of the
7 board of trustees. Initial terms of office shall commence upon approval by the Secretary of State
8 of the articles of incorporation.
9 (c) Reserved for future codification purposes.
